{"tid":1633027,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"經過昨日的教訓,今後不能再搞大遊行,絕不能搞","createTime":"2019-10-07T01:59:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T02:42:23.000Z","uid":281070,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"81cccc22b907b32985801aabce6373d8ee81966c","tid":1633027,"uid":281070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:59:34.000Z","msg":"明白有些人再想有過百萬人出來的偉大場面, 但這種場面不會再出現。<br />\n原因是警方不會再發不反對通知書, 群眾出來一陣佢已經可以清場。以往過百萬人的偉大場面是因為合法遊行, 警方比你由下午行到夜晚, 因為不斷有人KEEP住出, 咁就可以聚到好多好多人。<br />\n昨日的教訓告訴我們, 一旦多人聚集於某一區, 一旦鐵路網被封閉, 而巴士/小巴又會被查, 好多人就會走唔到比人拉, 損失慘重。<br />\n因此以後的行動<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">必須遍地開花</span></strong></span>, 多區同時行動, 而且<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">絕不能打陣地戰,一定要 HIT AND RUN, BE WATER</span></strong></span>。<br />\n好彩昨日下大雨, 導致少左人出港島, 不然被捕的人必然更多。<br />\nBTW, 個人對裝修有保留, 但如果真係要裝, 唔該對準中資/黑暴(如中國銀行), 唔好係藍店都裝, 尋日甚至中原都有人爆, 係過分左。"},{"pid":"59b73c1d36444547c6c9cd57c7d3e6c32e0a5596","tid":1633027,"uid":281070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:01:52.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"c595fb610d17943b0a4f866fba20193bf7687622","tid":1633027,"uid":299104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:02:34.000Z","msg":"明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3fy6PwF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3fy6PwF.png&h=ea9a012e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yYDlCk4w_-I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyYDlCk4w_-I&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4r%2F5csivkdzoxKq11rtKUO4%3D&h=515b9cdf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yYDlCk4w_-I</a><br />\n<br />\n關於民權法，要講清楚，美國並不要求大家和平<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632886\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/16328